{"tid":2341792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家香港係集中營，國安係獄卒，報國安就全部人死得快D","createTime":"2020-12-26T15:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T02:33:57.000Z","uid":154486,"like":50,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8c3f1f82ab0cabb5a66f860827d60e2028aff304","tid":2341792,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"而家我地全部人都坐緊監<br />\n國安係獄卒<br />\n<br />\n你去報國安，就越去依賴呢個監獄<br />\n越去依賴呢個監獄，你既自由就會縮得越快<br />\n因為你已經冇左自己解決問題既能力<br />\n<br />\n我地既自由已經冇乜，都遇左會縮到冇<br />\n但係可唔可以幫幫手減慢少少個速度<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">有乜野唔妥對方，唔該自己四四六六拆掂佢<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個post講得好好<br />\n龍門、印仔同木耳巴事件 睇出香港人嘅極大缺陷 比起極權 更討厭出位嘅同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2341548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2341548</a>"},{"pid":"b08b2d4ca2f3ec889795f6547167de3c396393e3","tid":2341792,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"一早就移民啦on9仔"},{"pid":"6b230af444b1197db3b4c33eb9a7207f6df20933","tid":2341792,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123b593acf1f6b6a539620a37320cbfd373a2f2d","tid":2341792,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b08b2d4ca2f3ec889795f6547167de3c396393e3","tid":2341792,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"一早就移民啦on9仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"請問有bno有閪屌(狗隻#237459)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aAtrJaV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aAtrJaV</a><br />\n#17 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論<br />\n<br />\n根本就唔關封關事,由始至終都係香港人攞嚟賤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2306128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.